---
title: My Life in Weeks
layout: layouts/base
---
<article class="container flow">
  <header class="flow prose-width">
    <h1>{{ title | safe }}</h1>
    <p>Ah, yes, I do love a combination data visualization/mortality reminder!</p>
    <p>A few implementations of this concept have popped up on the internet recently. Itâ€™s based on <a href="https://waitbutwhy.com/2014/05/life-weeks.html">a 2014 post by Tim Urban at Wait But Why</a> that presented some interesting ways to visualize your finitude. Then <a href="https://busterbenson.com/life-in-weeks">Buster Benson made one</a>. Most recently, I came across <a href="https://weeks.ginatrapani.org/">a version by Gina Trapani</a>.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="life-weeks-table">
    {% for week in lifeInWeeks %}
      {# Set tooltips #}
      {% set tooltip = "Week " ~ (week.index) ~ " / " ~ week.date %}

      {% if week.events.length %}
        {% set tooltip = tooltip + "<br>" %}
        {% for event in week.events %}
          {% set tooltip = tooltip + event.icon + " " + event.title %}
          {% if not loop.last %}{% set tooltip = tooltip + "<br>" %}{% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      {% endif %}

      {% if week.timespans.length %}
        {% set tooltip = tooltip + "<br>" %}
        {% for span in week.timespans %}
          {% set tooltip = tooltip + span.icon + " " + span.title %}
          {% if not loop.last %}{% set tooltip = tooltip + "<br>" %}{% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      {% endif %}

      <div
        class="week-box{% if week.isPast %} past{% endif %}"
        data-tippy-content="{{ tooltip | safe }}"
        tabindex="0"
      >
        {% for event in week.events %}
          {% if not event.hide_from_grid %}
            <span class="event-icon">{{ event.icon }}</span>
            <span class="event-title">{{ event.title }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</article>

<script src="https://unpkg.com/@popperjs/core@2"></script>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/tippy.js@6"></script>
<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
    tippy('.week-box', {
      allowHTML: true,
      placement: 'top',
      theme: 'light-border',
    });
  });
</script>
